  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '"Archery Game" is a Roguelite strategy game. Enemies spawn over time and
    try to kill you. You must avoid them and kill them, but your character can only
    attack while standing. The goal of the game is to survive as long as possible;
    the best score is recorded. You take damage if you collide with enemies. If you
    take enough damage, the game ends. The game gets progressively more difficult
    and different types of enemies appear. But don''t worry, if you kill enough enemies,
    you can level up. So choosing upgrades wisely is crucial

    Have fun!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0161d805a3764c089bef00bfe00793f5, type: 2}
